'''Turumme-warrens''' were large banks of apartment quarters built below the surface of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. These structures were usually owned by and built on top of underground manufacturing plants and were used to house the plants' workers.

Turumme-warrens got their name from the [[Turumme]], a [[Reptile/Legends|reptile]] that dug elaborate nests in the ground.

